  "content": "**Subject: Series A - AI Fintech - 140% Growth - Seeking Partners**\n\nDear [Investor Name],\n\nI noticed your recent investment in [Portfolio Company] and your focus on early-stage fintech. \nGiven your track record backing companies like theirs, I wanted to reach out about DataFlow Financial.\n\n\nWe're building AI-powered cash flow forecasting for mid-market companies, solving the $2.8B problem of poor financial visibility. \nOur platform provides intelligent insights based on hundreds of financial micro-interactions, helping CFOs reduce forecasting errors by 65%.\n\n\n**Traction highlights:**\n\u2022 \n$47K MRR, growing 140% year-over-year\n\n\u2022 38 enterprise clients including 2 Fortune 500s\n\u2022 \nRaised $1.8M seed from Catalyst Ventures last year\n\n\u2022 Former Head of Finance at Stripe leading go-to-market\n\n\nWe're raising our $8M Series A to expand our sales team and accelerate market penetration.\n \nThe round is 60% committed with participation from our existing investors and two new institutional VCs.\n\n\n\nYour investment thesis around B2B financial infrastructure aligns perfectly with our vision.\n Would you be interested in a 20-minute call to discuss the opportunity?\n\n\nI'd be happy to send our pitch deck if there's initial interest.\n\n\nBest regards,\nSarah Chen\nFounder & CEO, DataFlow Financial\nsarah@dataflow.com",
